title: (Wed Full) Who Rejected Bobby And Now He Wants To Put a Curse On Them + We Play The One Role Actors Game + Eddie's Kids Helping With Laundry Update
itunes:title: (Wed Full) Who Rejected Bobby And Now He Wants To Put a Curse On Them + We Play The One Role Actors Game + Eddie's Kids Helping With Laundry Update
description:
Bobby wants to put a curse on someone because they rejected coming on the show. Plus, we play the One Role Actors Game, where we name an actor and have to say the role they are most known for. Eddie shares an update on his kids starting to help with the laundry and how it's going.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
